 couldn't get him off the wall and trying hurt me even more. If I don't try, he shoots me with arrows. Anyone know how to get those darn wall-huggers out away from the wall?  <p>Durran Shadowstep!
~54 Halflin' Rogue
Rodcet Nife Server</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucoriscichemlock.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Coriscic Hemlock</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/31/01 1:00:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wall Huggers</span><hr size=1> I'm a pvp novice to say the least. It is often posible to still back stab a warrior with their back against a wall.  If you run right at them, then vere off to one side at the last minute and spin you can sometimes land a backstab even though there back is at the wall. If they turn towards its not going to happend, but its worked for me before.<br>
<br>
Another option would be to stock up on poisons and if the warrior wont get off the wall, run out of range of the arrows, apply poison and go poison him, rinse and repeat. It's probably going to make him come to you. <br>
<br>
Coriscic <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucoyoteblack.showPublicProfile?language=EN>coyoteblack</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/31/01 7:22:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wall Huggers</span><hr size=1>   Try jousting. You time the the looooong delay of there weps, and when they swing take off auto attack and step back. Then go inside with your low delay and poison.<br>
  Eventually the warrior will try and turn the tables on you and move up to time you when he does his back will be off the wall. Understandably this requires allot of luck and skill. Half the time I just apply poison hit him and run behind something, less honorable but bah!!! I hate loosing to a warrior. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showMessage?topicID=87.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showMessage?topicID=82.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.emailToFriend?topicID=91.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.threadControl?topicID=91.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=91.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=91.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousetheback